        [
          "Assamite Infiltrator pretending to be Nosferatu."
        ],
        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "“Kevin/Kensie Oscar” (Nour Rayyan) Assamite pretending to be a Nosferatu: They do not remember their lives before The Embrace. As far as they are concerned, they were born in Alamut, and have been trained as an unliving weapon. They’ve just been let out of Alamut with a single Objective: Use the current chaos in the Cainite society to Capture and Retrieve any and all traitors to the clan that they can. They have contacts prepared to take any they actually succeed in grabbing across the sea, but they have to get them there first. They are using their most advanced discipline, Obfuscate, to conceal their appearance, and are doing their best to make certain that no one in court has reason to go beyond that. They present themselves as a fledgling Nosferatu, new to the city, and afraid of almost everything, other Nosferatu included. They have enough lore of Clan and Camarilla to be able to pass a casual inspection of either, but they are playing a very dangerous game and know it, and they are prepared to die rather than reveal who sent them or why."
        ],
